Package: surveys
Title: Functions to assist with loading and analyzing surveys
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(as.person("Rick Wash <rick.wash@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"))
Description: Includes a number of functions that I commonly use to load and
   analyze surveys.  It can recognize a wide variety of question types, create
   scales of related items, etc.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: http://github.com/rwash/surveys
BugReports: http://github.com/rwash/surveys/issues
Imports: psy,
    gdata,
    ggplot2,
    grid
Suggests: testthat
